0 \to \Delta_p(A \cap B) \to \Delta_p(A) \oplus \Delta_p(B) \to^{(j^A \pi_1-j^B \pi_2)} \Delta_p^U(A \cup B) \to 0
j^A \pi_1-j^B \pi_2
(\phi_A, \phi_B)
w \in \Delta_p^U(A \cup B)
v= (\phi_A(w),-\phi_B(w)) 
(j^A \pi_1-j^B \pi_2)(v)=j^A \phi_A(w)+j^B \phi_B(w)=(\phi_A+\phi_B)(w)=1w=w.
\phi_A(w) \in \Delta_p(A)
w:\Delta_p \to A\cap B
\phi_A:A\cap B \to \Delta_p
\phi_A w:\Delta_p \to \Delta_p
